manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About Us OUR MISSION - Luggage that makes travel simple. We have focused on designing luggage that meets the travel needs of our customers. Our focus has and always will remain on our founding principles – Design, Innovation, Quality and Value. Back in the early days, we started as luggage importers, at that time luggage was bland, boxy, and generally black BORING! and this is when the vision was born. Our values and beliefs represent how we conduct ourselves throughout our supply chain and with colleagues, suppliers, customers and consumers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Make the most of your baggage weight allowance
reviews.reviewText: I love this It luggage because it is the lightest on the market and I'm able to pack more in my suitcase and stay within the baggage weight limits. I really need as much available weight for my personal items and souvineers during international travel. I highly recommend these for any traveler to get more for your money when flying.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It is a very nice luggage and fancy looking, I was scared because of the reviews but it turned out very nice. It looks very sturdy. But the one thing is the measure the size with the wheels, so technically this is a 26” luggage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Broken at First Trip.
reviews.reviewText: Not worth the money. The company says that they focus on quality and value in their mission statement. Yet it is obvious that unfortunately they do not. It broke after a single trip. There are better quality luggages that are just slightly more expensive.There are no options to refund or return the item either, nor can I find information on a warranty. Wish it didn't break so easily, or at least there was some kind of way to get it fixed. It is so pretty. I love the design and look, too bad it's not durable in the slightest.
